theorem Topology.P2_interior_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Topology.P2 (interior (closure A)) := by
  unfold Topology.P2
  intro x hx
  have hsubset : interior (closure A) ⊆ interior (closure (interior (closure A))) := by
    apply interior_mono
    intro y hy
    exact subset_closure hy
  exact hsubset hx

theorem Topology.P1_empty {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] :
    Topology.P1 (∅ : Set X) := by
  unfold Topology.P1
  intro x hx
  cases hx
